VOGEL, Appellant, v. WOLFF, Respondent. (Supreme Court, Appellate Division, First Department. March 27, 1914.) Action by H. G. Vogel against Harris Wolff. D. Bernstein, of New York City, for appellant. C. Goldzier, of New York City, for respondent

No opinion. Order affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements. Order filed.
